headline: Kenvue Ribbon-Cutting Marks Official Opening of New Global Headquarters in Summit, New Jersey
summary: SUMMIT, N.J., March 19, 2025--Today, Kenvue Inc. (NYSE: KVUE) held a ribbon-cutting ceremony for its new 290,000 sq. ft. global headquarters in Summit, New Jersey.
